text: Here’s everything Apple announced in the WWDC 2020 keynote today
Google employees demand company stop selling tech to police
President Trump signs executive order temporarily suspending work visas for H-1B holders
NYSE seeks SEC approval for more direct listings
Facebook acquires VR studio behind ‘Lone Echo’
Big outdoor brands join #StopHateForProfit campaign, boycott Facebook and Instagram ads
Apple unveils iOS 14 and macOS Big Sur features for India, China and other international markets
Apple’s iMessage update takes cues from Slack with mentions, pins, threads and more
Apple Maps gets electric vehicle routing to find EV chargers
Here’s how Apple’s stock fared during the WWDC keynote
Lyft settles DOJ lawsuit alleging violation of Americans with Disabilities Act
Apple will let you emulate old apps and run iOS apps on ARM Macs
Hulu announces a new offer-focused ad format called GatewayGo
Apple is releasing a Mac mini with an Apple processor for developers starting this week
Watch the first trailer for ‘Foundation,’ coming to Apple TV+ in 2021
Apple adds a dedicated biking feature to Maps in iOS 14
Apple’s Safari will soon tell you all the ad trackers watching you
Microsoft kills Mixer, will push users to Facebook Gaming
Apple is building its own processors for future Macs
Apple will let users pick their own default email and browser apps
Equity Monday: Heartbest and Acquire raise capital as tech turns to Apple’s WWDC
Microsoft confirms acquisition of CyberX to boost security in its Azure IoT business
Extra Crunch Live: Join Inspired Capital’s Alexa von Tobel for a live Q&A on June 25 at 2 pm EDT/11 am PDT
